{"tid":990634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民主黨宣布反水貨客　下周遊行","createTime":"2019-01-21T17:59:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T15:25:27.000Z","uid":47714,"like":5,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"c21e3ea7210881f7082c877eb0970a28017567c8","tid":990634,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T17:59:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/民主黨下周日遊行反水貨-倡-一周一行-變-一年八行/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E9%BB%A8%E4%B8%8B%E5%91%A8%E6%97%A5%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%E5%8F%8D%E6%B0%B4%E8%B2%A8-%E5%80%A1-%E4%B8%80%E5%91%A8%E4%B8%80%E8%A1%8C-%E8%AE%8A-%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4%E5%85%AB%E8%A1%8C%2F&d=LP25UddgDlQPT8s18mXU6dibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=d9025ee3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E9%BB%A8%E4%B8%8B%E5%91%A8%E6%97%A5%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%E5%8F%8D%E6%B0%B4%E8%B2%A8-%E5%80%A1-%E4%B8%80%E5%91%A8%E4%B8%80%E8%A1%8C-%E8%AE%8A-%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4%E5%85%AB%E8%A1%8C%2F&h=8f121922\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/society/民主黨下周日遊行反水貨-倡-一周一行-變-一年八行/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/609D8F84-3EE9-460C-882D-807F134EA353_mw1024_s_n_tUQsw_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F609D8F84-3EE9-460C-882D-807F134EA353_mw1024_s_n_tUQsw_1200x0.png&h=d39ff3f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n北區水貨客問題有漸趨嚴重之勢。民主黨宣布，將於下周日（27日）發起「反水貨遊行」，要求政府限制內地自由行來港次數，由現時「一周一行」改為「一年八行」。另外，人口政策關注組召集人譚凱邦則提倡，推行「半年一行」甚至「一年一行」。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨指，上周電話訪問，87%受訪者認為水貨活動有影響其日常生活。該黨稱電話訪問中有七成民民都支持「一年八行」的建議。民主黨亦將在下星期日（1月27日）發起「反水貨遊行」。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，人口政策關注組今日於旺角街頭舉行論壇，召集人譚凱邦則要求將「一周一行」政策，起碼改為「半年一行」甚至「一年一行」，以減少一日來回的「嫌惡性」自由行。"},{"pid":"d5fc1a1039df3bc4941082fffef5ba683128bdb2","tid":990634,"uid":64374,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T18:27:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8672074d1f4332f42a2489bea81a269296dad91f","tid":990634,"uid":44559,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T18:28:49.000Z","msg":"而家先反?<br />\n<br />\n本土派幾多年前做左野?"},{"pid":"5fab60de7626f13073d06a19a0256ce76de20c35","tid":990634,"uid":35430,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T18:30:21.000Z","msg":"幾年前屌完光復行動今日黎呃飯食？"},{"pid":"c3740e8662ff4b179b7c50cf71cd64e229fcbf6f","tid":990634,"uid":52276,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T18:35:24.000Z","msg":"收皮啦！阻礙經濟發展民主派食屎大"},{"pid":"e4b3ba182789e65d2082f87ad12555527cd4fc39","tid":990634,"uid":30006,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T18:52:30.000Z","msg":"客你老味<br />\n<br />\n叫走私犯"},{"pid":"f188050db85288421a0663fe5ec1a1a13db93b6b","tid":990634,"uid":51701,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T20:08:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rQnqKxt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrQnqKxt.jpg&h=71571d11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本是同根生"},{"pid":"0598ad5ad1cf59f66dbb1655886b314a655b95c7","tid":990634,"uid":36901,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T20:14:20.000Z","msg":"旅客陸路離境稅<br />\n每次$300<br />\n有冇得諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1ef31802bf5f5653787cf0951a3c0d71815d4ea","tid":990634,"uid":20867,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T20:25:46.000Z","msg":"系時候考驗本土派選民既智商<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"473009b7e1de0a2d4fe36e39677eb095d764c7db","tid":990634,"uid":31841,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T20:50:00.000Z","msg":"哩D就真係食人血饅頭喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"523a2d2b652bb685430298456050c242c434db25","tid":990634,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T